## 🛠️ Installation

### **Requirements**
- Python 3.11+
- 50MB disk space
- Terminal access

### **Install from PyPI**
```bash
pip install om-cli
```

### **Install from Source**
```bash
git clone https://github.com/frism/om.git
cd om
pip install -r requirements.txt
python setup.py install
```

### **Verify Installation**
```bash
om --version
om --help
om qm
```

